{"tid":2374544,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[銀包撚]四歲嘅馬臀皮 手作銀包分享（歡迎同好一齊分享）","createTime":"2021-01-21T10:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T11:29:40.000Z","uid":199436,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3046e0c7ffa3c95466133b257a01e0ff60cad2","tid":2374544,"uid":199436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"四年前係台灣呢間【Mister手作】訂左個馬臀皮銀包，價錢公道，手勢又好，攞到已經勁中意。<br />\n而家個銀包四歲生日，俾大家望下佢咩樣。（利申，完全係粗用)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51k84GL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51k84GL.jpg&h=ce9453da&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個係四年前攞到嘅時候影嘅。<br />\n個色個陣會係湖水藍嘅感覺。<br />\n跟住越用，個色慢慢變深，而家係深海藍嘅感覺，一樣好靚，但係唔係好影到出來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDsGFf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDsGFf6.jpg&h=0f4d0121&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3e2pHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3e2pHM.jpg&h=00e0e35b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KsnfKHP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsnfKHP.jpg&h=7335256d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且我呢個完全唔似我之前用嘅濕鳩銀包，用一用個皮邊又開裂啊又甩皮啊又咩又物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37xrRoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37xrRoP.jpg&h=1716c93e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4K9Pat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4K9Pat.jpg&h=7eca84f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個我真心可以用幾十年，越來越期待佢之後變化！！<br />\n有冇一樣中意手作皮件嘅巴打絲打分享下自己個銀包！！"},{"pid":"0ccf242ff15228bf03ca520e3047408d252de0d1","tid":2374544,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"邊間cordovan?<br />\n你點養？cordovan正常使用會花，但可修復"},{"pid":"fb94334fabf58893a3048c8d08d0181d5d45464e","tid":2374544,"uid":199436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ccf242ff15228bf03ca520e3047408d252de0d1","tid":2374544,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"邊間cordovan?<br />\n你點養？cordovan正常使用會花，但可修復"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"我呢個係新禧，<br />\n完全求其用，但係我係擺後袋，唔多會掂到硬野"},{"pid":"274032cf50cae7bf5d2980667df465e8cf759c15","tid":2374544,"uid":2297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"幾錢個?<br />\n放埋錢同卡之後會唔會好厚?"},{"pid":"f81b7ec9d85d320e7f04830ba35d25fb7bc09d7f","tid":2374544,"uid":199436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274032cf50cae7bf5d2980667df465e8cf759c15","tid":2374544,"uid":2297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"幾錢個?<br />\n放埋錢同卡之後會唔會好厚?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:05:00.000Z","msg":"呢個兩千幾，唔會話好厚啊。馬臀皮貴野來~"},{"pid":"fa0c49a4cd5280c831fb63ca4cf873a8201f567e","tid":2374544,"uid":75929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ccf242ff15228bf03ca520e3047408d252de0d1","tid":2374544,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"邊間cordovan?<br />\n你點養？cordovan正常使用會花，但可修復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"請問有花點修復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1999456550ae534b5930637a9c7e798630e2757a","tid":2374544,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0c49a4cd5280c831fb63ca4cf873a8201f567e","tid":2374544,"uid":75929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ccf242ff15228bf03ca520e3047408d252de0d1","tid":2374544,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"邊間cordovan?<br />\n你點養？cordovan正常使用會花，但可修復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"請問有花點修復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited